		<description><![CDATA[I have always used my pinkie since i started playing although i experience pain in it sometimes when stretching.
I have also done that very thing where you put your thumb to the side although there was a guy on Youtube who said it was a natural position to take the strain away.
I sometimes get pain in my thumb when playing so maybe i am pressing too hard on the neck.
I also end up in a ridiculous position with my thumb when i play higher up the neck where my thumb bends around into an uncomfortable position, Any tips ?]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have always used my pinkie since i started playing although i experience pain in it sometimes when stretching.<br />
I have also done that very thing where you put your thumb to the side although there was a guy on Youtube who said it was a natural position to take the strain away.<br />
I sometimes get pain in my thumb when playing so maybe i am pressing too hard on the neck.<br />
I also end up in a ridiculous position with my thumb when i play higher up the neck where my thumb bends around into an uncomfortable position, Any tips ?</p>
